{"color": "green", "emoji": "\ud83d\udcac", "event_type": "Agent Message", "message": "The confirmation schema already knows how to propose beat refinements from chat. I\u2019m checking the deterministic action policy and any snapshot serializers next, because the new edit path needs to respect the same guardrails and expose ri...", "raw_event": {"item": {"id": "item_22", "text": "The confirmation schema already knows how to propose beat refinements from chat. I\u2019m checking the deterministic action policy and any snapshot serializers next, because the new edit path needs to respect the same guardrails and expose richer beat metadata back to the frontend without leaking persistence details.", "type": "agent_message"}, "type": "item.completed"}, "task_display_context": {"event_number": 44, "prompt_index": 50, "prompt_name": "49 \u2014 Beat Sheet Refinement UI and Chat Controls", "prompt_total": 100}, "timestap": "2026-04-02T00:22:17-07:00"}
