{"color": "green", "emoji": "\ud83d\udcac", "event_type": "Agent Message", "message": "I have enough context to set the implementation direction. Plan: 1. Extend the beat-sheet model and serializer to carry durable edit metadata: per-beat stage notes, edit history, \u201cmaterial change\u201d classification, and downstream refresh s...", "raw_event": {"item": {"id": "item_37", "text": "I have enough context to set the implementation direction.\n\nPlan:\n1. Extend the beat-sheet model and serializer to carry durable edit metadata: per-beat stage notes, edit history, \u201cmaterial change\u201d classification, and downstream refresh status.\n2. Add a dedicated backend edit endpoint that patches a saved beat revision in place, records a structured user-edit event, and invalidates composition/audio/finalize when the edit is materially structural.\n3. Wire the workspace to that endpoint and rebuild the beats stage around a living editor: per-beat fields, quick refinement presets, change history, and visible downstream refresh cues.\n4. Expand chat/action echo coverage and tests so UI edits, backend events, and chat-triggered refinements stay synchronized.\n5. Run targeted backend/frontend tests, then do browser-based QA with the Docker Compose app and capture screenshots before writing the required summary file.", "type": "agent_message"}, "type": "item.completed"}, "task_display_context": {"event_number": 73, "prompt_index": 50, "prompt_name": "49 \u2014 Beat Sheet Refinement UI and Chat Controls", "prompt_total": 100}, "timestap": "2026-04-02T00:22:50-07:00"}
