 belonging.\"\n321-                    ),\n322-                    bedtime_notes=(\n323-                        \"Each pressure beat is kept soft, visible, and quickly buffered by \"\n324-                        \"companionship.\"\n325-                    ),\n326-                    beats=[\n327-                        GeneratedBeatSheetBeat(\n328-                            key=key,\n329-                            label=label,\n330-                            summary=(\n331-                                f\"{label} keeps the harbor story high level, concrete, and \"\n332-                                \"bedtime-ready.\"\n333-                            ),\n334-                            emotional_intent=(\n335-                                f\"{label} should feel calm, clear, and emotionally readable.\"\n336-                            ),\n337-                            bedtime_softening_note=(\n338-                                f\"{label} stays bedtime-safe by keeping tension gentle and \"\n339-                                \"quickly soothed.\"\n340-                            ),\n341-                        )\n342-                        for key, label in (\n343-                            (\"opening_image\", \"Opening Image\"),\n344-                            (\"theme_stated\", \"Theme Stated\"),\n345-                            (\"set_up\", \"Set-Up\"),\n346-                            (\"catalyst\", \"Catalyst\"),\n347-                            (\"debate\", \"Debate\"),\n348-                            (\"break_into_two\", \"Break into Two\"),\n349-                            (\"b_story\", \"B Story\"),\n350-                            (\"fun_and_games\", \"Fun and Games\"),\n351-                            (\"midpoint\", \"Midpoint\"),\n352-                            (\"bad_guys_close_in\", \"Bad Guys Close In\"),\n353-                            (\"all_is_lost\", \"All Is Lost\"),\n354-                            (\"dark_night_of_the_soul\", \"