{"color": "green", "emoji": "\ud83d\udcac", "event_type": "Agent Message", "message": "Implemented the beat-sheet refinement flow end to end and committed the production changes as `ce7254d` with message `feat(prompt-49): beat sheet refinement ui and chat`. The main outcome is a new durable beat editor with per-beat/top-le...", "raw_event": {"item": {"id": "item_227", "text": "Implemented the beat-sheet refinement flow end to end and committed the production changes as `ce7254d` with message `feat(prompt-49): beat sheet refinement ui and chat`.\n\nThe main outcome is a new durable beat editor with per-beat/top-level edits, persisted edit history, chat/action-echo sync, and downstream refresh invalidation when the accepted beat sheet changes. Backend support landed in [sessions.py](/Users/kevin/code/storyteller/backend/app/services/sessions.py), [session.py](/Users/kevin/code/storyteller/backend/app/models/session.py), [session_hydration.py](/Users/kevin/code/storyteller/backend/app/services/session_hydration.py), and the new route in [sessions.py](/Users/kevin/code/storyteller/backend/app/api/v1/routes/sessions.py). Frontend work landed in [BeatSheetStage.tsx](/Users/kevin/code/storyteller/frontend/src/features/session/BeatSheetStage.tsx), [SessionWorkspacePage.tsx](/Users/kevin/code/storyteller/frontend/src/pages/session/SessionWorkspacePage.tsx), [sessions.ts](/Users/kevin/code/storyteller/frontend/src/api/sessions.ts), and [index.css](/Users/kevin/code/storyteller/frontend/src/styles/index.css). I also updated the workflow invalidation graph so beat edits now refresh `story_setup` as downstream planning.\n\nVerification completed:\n- `pytest backend/tests` -> `166 passed, 5 skipped`\n- `npm test` in `frontend/` -> `14 passed`, `76 passed`\n- `npm run lint` -> passed\n- `npm run build` -> passed\n- Browser QA against the compose stack using a seeded live session:\n  - desktop before/after: [prompt-49-beat-editor-desktop-before.png](/Users/kevin/code/storyteller/.artifacts/webapp-qa/prompt-49-beat-editor-desktop-before.png), [prompt-49-beat-editor-desktop-after.png](/Users/kevin/code/storyteller/.artifacts/webapp-qa/prompt-49-beat-editor-desktop-after.png)\n  - focused editor captures: [prompt-49-beat-editor-desktop-focused.png](/Users/kevin/code/storyteller/.artifacts/webapp-qa/prompt-49-beat-editor-desktop-focused.png), [prompt-49-beat-editor-mobile-focused.png](/Users/kevin/code/storyteller/.artifacts/webapp-qa/prompt-49-beat-editor-mobile-focused.png)\n\nThe required reviewer summary was written as the final file action at [summary.md](/Users/kevin/code/storyteller/.yolopilot/runs/20260331T205548_storyteller_prompt_pack/49_beat_sheet_refinement_ui_and_chat_controls/summary.md).", "type": "agent_message"}, "type": "item.completed"}, "task_display_context": {"event_number": 433, "prompt_index": 50, "prompt_name": "49 \u2014 Beat Sheet Refinement UI and Chat Controls", "prompt_total": 100}, "timestap": "2026-04-02T01:06:14-07:00"}
